            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"太和站月台擠滿候車乘客。梁國峰攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6037491fdac332ef44edf53e0c22ad7a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250205/_2025020509440983798.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">太和站月台擠滿候車乘客。梁國峰攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今晨（5日）港鐵太和站附近有工程車故障，東鐵綫全綫服務受阻，列車班次延誤最少4分鐘至24分鐘不等；太和站亦只能使用1號月台上落客，個別出入口關閉實施人流管制，月台擠滿候車乘客。受故障影響，有女學生直言在車廂內「等咗好耐」，列車一直未能開出，以致最終上學遲到。亦有乘客知道事故後提早一個半小時出門，但期間亦「等咗幾班車」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060172/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"陳女士知道東鐵錢事故後，提早一個半小時出門，惟期間「等咗幾班車」。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2f2079b1bcdf0f465638ebb959abb2eb/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_085253924_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳女士知道東鐵錢事故後，提早一個半小時出門，惟期間「等咗幾班車」。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060171/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"莊同學因東鐵綫事故，上學遲到。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5c90b4daa6d1f9cde8765de980dc1a01/2025-02/1_1