ypeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車站人頭湧湧。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060147/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9d352831a881dbb06f4c9fdb957d86eb/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_080121074_09_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060148/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/af14f6fbfd0956791c66130fbdf854d1/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_080121074_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060137/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"太和站關閉個別出入口，實施人流管理措施。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/29b835b38eda00a3051b4fe43faee75a/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_080121074_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        太和站關閉個別出入口，實施人流管理措施。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>列車服務受阻期間正值今早上班上學繁亡時間，姓莊女學生由上水乘搭列車前往太和站，原本需要早上9時返回學校，惟遇上列車受阻，她最終遲到。她形容：「企喺車廂等咗好耐，5、6分鐘都有，有廣播話出現故障。」不過她指遲到15分鐘左右，相信老師知道事故也會體諒。\n\n</p>\n<p>乘客阮女士由粉嶺出發到太和站上班，她到達粉嶺站後聽到廣播，才知太和站發生事故。她指行程「好似往時咁樣，不過啲車就隔疏咗」。她說整個安排沒有混亂，「同平時返工差不多，去到車站等咗兩分鐘就有車，不過比平時返工呢段時間，粉嶺車站的確多咗人。」雖然今日列車服務有延誤，但她仍能趕及上班，沒有遲到。\n\n</p>\n<p>另一名乘客陳女士，由港島東區乘搭列車到太和站，相約友人行山。她指今晨知道東鐵綫出現事故後，提早一個半小時出門，其間亦「等咗幾班車」。她又認為事故期間港鐵職員指示清晰，亦有效疏導人流，對自己影響不算太大。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060120/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"肇事工程車停在三渡坑巴士站對開路軌上，工程人員設法將其移走。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/52b784cdb923a0d4f39c17009b31b64e/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_074552249.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        肇事工程車停在三渡坑巴士站對開路軌上，工程人員設法將其移走。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060121/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/863fd66b7e779c5215b3eeb69ad94ced/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_074552249_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">