ield--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060125/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/06a2458ed6d1ee1842d4e44fe61e0338/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_074552249_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060126/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/74e16a16efa2d8c660abf9a86b49ae38/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_074552249_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060129/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1c45bd2453d61ebc7e46e02416ce0511/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_074552249_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>港鐵於今日（5日）清晨5時21分宣布，由於東鐵綫太和站附近有工程車出現設備故障，東鐵綫列車服務需要調整。東鐵綫來往金鐘站至大埔墟站每8分鐘一班車；來往大埔墟站至羅湖站及落馬洲站每35分鐘一班。其後至8時02分，港鐵更新班次調整，來往金鐘站至火炭站每4分鐘一班；來往火炭站至大埔墟站每8分鐘一班；來往大埔墟站至羅湖站每16分鐘一班；來往上水站至落馬洲站每24分鐘一班。\n\n</p>\n<p>現場所見，工程車停在三渡坑巴士站對開路軌上，工程人員在現場處理，設法將故障工程車移離行車綫。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060111/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"太和站附近有工程車出現設備故障，東鐵綫列車服務受阻。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e46cce3e40f7acb86a862a5e4908479d/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_073900933.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        太和站附近有工程車出現設備故障，東鐵綫列車服務受阻。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060112/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/76eca2228e153e2c0eab1ac4438f9619/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_073900933_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060114/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"太和站附近有工程車設備故障，東鐵綫服務受阻。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/90894ff032ffdf3080d88a4b93880d80/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_073900933_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        太和站附近有工程車設備故障，東鐵綫服務受阻。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060115/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5d8a1276548d759b11d516c686b49085/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_073900933_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060116/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9dc14108e4c4743b2a8ca3f9122585ed/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_073900933_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060118/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3538c16e55a3492f31e8c17b7a863e8e/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250205_073900933_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<